#1 角色參考圖（白底）
A clean character model reference sheet showing the same single character repeated across the sheet as a full-body front, three-quarter, side and back turnaround plus a row of head-and-shoulders expression studies, rendered in the naturalistic hand-drawn 2D idiom of Satoshi Kon's Paprika (Madhouse; character design Masashi Ando): realistic human proportions and a naturalistic face, clean fine evenly-weighted ink linework with no rough or variable brush texture, soft flat cel shading with only subtle tonal gradients and no hard-edged chiaroscuro. Pure solid white background #FFFFFF, uniform and empty, no environment, no props, no ground shadow, no vignette. Even neutral front studio lighting, no coloured cast, no moody grade, no atmosphere, true local colours fully legible. Figures evenly spaced and consistently scaled, full figure uncropped in every pose, identical costume, hair and proportions across all views. Flat, documentary, reference-accurate, not cinematic.

#2 場景參考圖（人物中性）
A wide establishing scene plate of a single location, rendered in the naturalistic hand-drawn 2D idiom of Satoshi Kon's Paprika (Madhouse; art direction Nobutaka Ike): dense photoreal hand-painted background, clean fine evenly-weighted ink linework, soft painterly cel shading with subtle gradients rather than hard-edged chiaroscuro, any surreal element rendered with the same photographic fidelity and perspective logic as ordinary reality. Reflective surfaces and glass read as quiet thresholds. Cinematic wide vertical 9:16 composition, accurate architecture and depth, restrained and melancholic, atmosphere over spectacle. Colours full-bodied and luminous, never muddy or grimy-desaturated.

#3 道具參考圖（白底）
A clean product reference sheet showing the same single object from multiple angles — front, three-quarter, side and top — plus one small detail or exploded callout, rendered in the naturalistic hand-drawn 2D idiom of Satoshi Kon's Paprika (Madhouse): clean fine evenly-weighted ink linework, soft flat cel shading with subtle gradients and accurate material rendering of metal and plastic, no hard-edged chiaroscuro. Pure solid white background #FFFFFF, uniform and empty, no environment, no ground shadow, no vignette. Even neutral studio lighting, no coloured cast, no moody grade, true local colours fully legible. Views evenly spaced and consistently scaled, each angle uncropped and crisp. Flat, documentary, reference-accurate, not cinematic.

#4 Storyboard（彩色keyframe）
A single cinematic storyboard keyframe in a 9:16 vertical frame, rendered in the naturalistic hand-drawn 2D idiom of Satoshi Kon's Paprika (Madhouse; character design Masashi Ando, art direction Nobutaka Ike): realistic proportions and naturalistic faces, clean fine evenly-weighted ink linework, soft painterly cel shading with subtle gradients rather than hard-edged chiaroscuro, dense photoreal painted background, surreal elements rendered with the same photographic fidelity as reality. Clear staging and depth with readable eyelines and foreground / midground / background separation, reflective surfaces as thresholds, restrained and melancholic, never muddy or grimy-desaturated.

